<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>Dinamika Food Service</title>
  <style>
    * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
    body {
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f4f1ea;
      color: #3e2a47;
      line-height: 1.6;
      overflow-x: hidden;
      position: relative;
    }

    .middle-bg {
      position: absolute;
      top: 25%;
      left: 0;
      width: 100%;
      height: 600px;
      background-image: url('images/background.jpg');
      background-size: cover;
      background-position: center;
      opacity: 0.12;
      z-index: -1;
      pointer-events: none;
    }

    nav {
      position: fixed;
      top: 0;
      left: 0;
      background-color: #6d4c41;
      padding: 15px;
      text-align: center;
      width: 200px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      z-index: 1000;
    }

    nav ul {
      list-style: none;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      padding: 0;
    }

    nav ul li {
      margin: 10px 0;
    }

    nav ul li a {
      text-decoration: none;
      color: white;
      font-size: 18px;
      font-weight: 600;
      transition: color 0.3s ease, transform 0.3s ease;
    }

    nav ul li a:hover {
      color: #ffb74d;
      transform: scale(1.05);
    }

    .action-btn {
      position: fixed;
      right: 20px;
      background-color: #6d4c41;
      color: white;
      padding: 10px 18px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: bold;
      font-size: 16px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
      transition: background-color 0.3s ease, transform 0.3s ease;
      z-index: 1000;
    }

    .action-btn:hover {
      background-color: #5e4031;
      transform: scale(1.05);
    }

    .admin-panel-btn { top: 15px; }
    .logout-btn { top: 65px; }

    .container {
      max-width: 1200px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 10px 20px 20px 20px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .logo {
      max-width: 400px;
      margin-top: -40px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      display: block;
      margin-left: auto;
      margin-right: auto;
    }

    header {
      margin-bottom: 40px;
    }

    header h1 {
      font-size: 48px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #3e2a47;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      text-shadow: 2px 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
    }

    header p {
      font-size: 20px;
      color: #3e2a47;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
      text-shadow: 1px 1px 3px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
    }

    .cta {
      background-color: #6d4c41;
      color: #fff;
      padding: 15px 25px;
      border-radius: 5px;
      font-size: 18px;
      font-weight: 600;
      display: inline-block;
      text-decoration: none;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
      transition: background-color 0.3s ease, transform 0.3s ease;
    }

    .cta:hover {
      background-color: #5e4031;
      transform: scale(1.05);
    }

    .services {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 40px;
      margin: 40px 0;
    }

    .service-item {
      background-color: #fff;
      padding: 30px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      width: 30%;
      text-align: center;
      transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
    }

    .service-item:hover {
      transform: translateY(-10px) scale(1.02);
      box-shadow: 0 8px 12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
    }

    .service-item h3 {
      color: #6d4c41;
      font-size: 24px;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
    }

    .service-item p {
      color: #6d4c41;
      font-size: 18px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .contact-info {
      margin-top: 20px;
      font-size: 18px;
      color: #6d4c41;
    }

    .contact-info strong {
      color: #3e2a47;
    }

    footer {
      margin-top: 50px;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #aaa;
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .services {
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 20px;
      }

      .service-item {
        width: 100%;
      }

      nav {
        top: 10px;
        left: 50%;
        transform: translateX(-50%);
      }

      .action-btn {
        right: 10px;
        padding: 8px 14px;
        font-size: 14px;
      }

      .admin-panel-btn { top: 10px; }
      .logout-btn { top: 55px; }
    }

    .animate-fade {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(20px);
      transition: opacity 0.8s ease, transform 0.8s ease;
    }

    .animate-show {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateY(0);
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <div class="middle-bg"></div>

  <% if (isAdmin) { %>
    <a href="/admin020504" class="action-btn admin-panel-btn">üîÅ Admin Panel</a>
    <a href="/logout" class="action-btn logout-btn">üö™ Logout</a>
  <% } else { %>
    <a href="/login" class="action-btn admin-panel-btn">üîê Admin</a>
  <% } %>

  <nav class="animate-fade">
    <ul>
      <li><a href="/">Home</a></li>
      <li><a href="/blog">Blog</a></li>
      <li><a href="/about">About Us</a></li>
      <li><a href="/contact">Contact</a></li>
    </ul>
  </nav>

  <div class="container animate-fade">
    <img src="images/LOGO DINAMIKA FIX.png" alt="Logo Dinamika Food Service" class="logo">

    <header>
      <h1>Selamat datang di Dinamika Food Service</h1>
      <p>Partner terpercaya Anda dalam menyediakan layanan katering berkualitas tinggi.</p>
    </header>

    <a href="/menu" class="cta">Jelajahi Menu Kami</a>

    <div class="services">
      <div class="service-item animate-fade">
        <h3>Snack</h3>
        <p>Camilan lezat dan beragam untuk acara Anda.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="service-item animate-fade">
        <h3>Nasi Box</h3>
        <p>Box makan lengkap dengan bahan berkualitas tinggi.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="service-item animate-fade">
        <h3>Prasmanan</h3>
        <p>Layanan prasmanan dengan berbagai pilihan menu.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="contact-info animate-fade">
      <p>Untuk informasi lebih lanjut, hubungi kami di: <strong>088225947063</strong></p>
    </div>

    <footer class="animate-fade">
      <p>&copy; 2025 Dinamika Food Service | Semua Hak Cipta Dilindungi</p>
    </footer>
  </div>

  <script>
    window.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', () => {
      document.querySelectorAll('.animate-fade').forEach(el => {
        setTimeout(() => {
          el.classList.add('animate-show');
        }, 200);
      });
    });
  </script>
</body>
</html>
